                  </persName> was indicted<rs id="t18461026-2154-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18461026-2154-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18461026-2154-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp> for stealing 3 pints of oil, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.4<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., the goods of the <persName id="t18461026-name-890" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18461026-name-890" type="gender" value="indeterminate"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18461026-2154-offence-1 t18461026-name-890"></join>General Steam Navigation Company</persName>, in a certain vessel on the river Thames.</rs>
